weight: 400;\">It allows you to create a truly branded experience for customers.</span></p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-double-right fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is useful to be able to gather usage-related data.</span></p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-double-right fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Experience Cloud sites are mobile-friendly, making sure better customer satisfaction and improving customer retention.</span></p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-double-right fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The chatter feature is extremely beneficial for alerting co-workers that their attention is needed on a particular case or work order. </span></p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-angle-double-right fas\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce has a great search feature. Finding what you are searching for is pretty simple. You can search by a work order number, customer number, name, contact name, and many other things.</span></p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-12 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-one\" style=\"--awb-font-size:30px;\"><h1 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;--fontSize:30;--minFontSize:30;line-height:var